  "notes": "Root element has three classes: 'block', 'block-layout-builder', and 'block-field-blocknodenews-articlefield-n-media' — all must be present. The picture element uses four source elements for responsive breakpoints: wide (min-width: 1280px), desktop (min-width: 1024px), tablet (min-width: 768px), and mobile (default). The img element always uses loading='eager', width='375', height='211' (mobile fallback dimensions). The figcaption is present only when a caption is provided. A companion selector .block-field-blocknodepagefield-b-media follows the same structure for page nodes.",
